9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Rob-B-Hood | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"For never-do-well compulsive gambler Fong, there's only one thing more fearsome than debtors at his doorstep - having to coax a crying baby. But what if the baby becomes his golden goose to fend off his debtors? Can he overcome his phobia of diapers, milk bottles, and cloying lullabies?"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/108379/rob-b-hood"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Rob-B-Hood"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"For never-do-well compulsive gambler Fong, there's only one thing more fearsome than debtors at his doorstep - having to coax a crying baby. But what if the baby becomes his golden goose to fend off his debtors? Can he overcome his phobia of diapers, milk bottles, and cloying lullabies?"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/108379/rob-b-hood"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aJZ8i1KEy5Kdc6hXNlLiHOlhdTA.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Rob-B-Hood"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"For never-do-well compulsive gambler Fong, there's only one thing more fearsome than debtors at his doorstep - having to coax a crying baby. But what if the baby becomes his golden goose to fend off his debtors? Can he overcome his phobia of diapers, milk bottles, and cloying lullabies?"}],["$","meta","13",{"name":"twitter:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aJZ8i1KEy5Kdc6hXNlLiHOlhdTA.